description:
Sodium Hydroxide Chemigram I - 4K

Made by hand on light sensitive photographic paper with darkroom chemicals. The characteristic marks of this piece was produced with pellets of a strong alkaline (drain cleaner!). I think the violence of this process shows through the chemigram. The final piece was scanned and this image is high resolution 4K.
